  "texts": [
    "In order to test the user's recollection and comprehension, the flow chart -6 model above makes sure that the questions are focused on important details.",
    "The language model then goes over and improves both kinds of questions to make sure they are accurate and clear.",
    "Lastly, the questions are arranged such that users can interact with them in a format appropriate for learning sessions or quizzes.",
